          King, denoted as RFR. Let's saw Colleen folds on a Jack, and calls on a Queen of King,
          denoted FCC.
        </p>
        <p>
          If both players are committed to these strategies, what are Rowans expected net winnings?  (Note that all
          the above hand pairs are equally likely, what are Rowan's net winnings in each case?)
        </p>
      </statement>
    </task>
